RESTUFL ROUTES

Rest- HTTP Routes and CRUD

Two types of HTTP Routes:
GET and POST

CREATE
READ
UPDATE
DESTROY

Name:   url:                  type:    Description:

INDEX   /campgrounds          GET      Shows List of Campgrounds
NEW     /campgrounds/new      GET      Shows new form for creating campgrounds
CREATE  /campgrounds          POST     Ceate a new campground, redirects back to original page
SHOW    /campgrounds/:id      GET      Shows information about campgrounds
EDIT    /campgrounds/:id/edit GET      Shows edit form for campgrounds
UPDATE  /campgrounds/:id      PUT      Updates current information on infopage, redirects back to info page 
DESTRY  /campgrounds/:id      DEL      Deletes forms/info for campgrounds

